{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, we were loaded into cattle cars that I think people are familiar with-- very crowded, no food, no water, a bucket for toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, we stopped at a couple of railroad stations-- I don't know in what German towns-- where kids were out there on the platforms throwing rocks at us in Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But another one of those coincidences happened was when the train crossed the German border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It stopped, and the doors were flung open, and we heard a German going back and forth yelling, women and children out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there weren't that many children left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I walked out with my mother, walking along the railroad track.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was 13.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, for no reason whatsoever, I thought maybe I better stay with my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was a little older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was not all that well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, mom, I'm going to go back on the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she said fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She didn't know what was right or wrong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I jumped back on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She went on by herself, and which was very smart and very lucky.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because that very night, all the women who did have children were selected with the children for elimination at Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I lost my grandmother, and I lost two of my aunts and my good friends, my cousins that I grew up with on that night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Had I gone with my mother, both of us would have been dead also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But she survived in Stuffhof, and she was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she eventually found me in Italy and died in Los Angeles 12 years ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to a camp which was a division of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not really Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The actual camp was called Kaufering, Kaufering Eins.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
